Ques.1: Find the number of Artists in the studio (without a HAVING clause).
Query : SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM employees
        WHERE role = 'Artist';

Ques.2: Find the number of Employees of each role in the studio.
Query : SELECT role, COUNT(*)
        FROM employees  
        GROUP BY role;

Ques.3: Find the total number of years employed by all Engineers.
Query : SELECT SUM(years_employed)
        FROM employees
        WHERE role = 'Engineer';
